      "identifier": "ea:concept:speech-datasets",
      "name": "Speech Datasets",
      "abstract": "Speech datasets turn individual voice recordings into reviewable, documented and reusable collections without erasing the conditions of capture.",
      "description": "Speech datasets are structured collections of recorded speech, transcripts, speaker context and quality metadata prepared for analysis, preservation or downstream machine-learning workflows.",
